      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">東方未明.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>東方未明，顛倒衣裳。顛之倒之，自公召之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Before the east was bright,
I was putting on my clothes upside down ;
I was putting them on upside down,
And there was one from the court calling me.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
