      <prop type="x-translation-ref">東方未明.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>東方未晞，顛倒裳衣。倒之顛之，自公令之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Before there was a streak of claw-n in the east,
I was putting on my clothes upside down;
I was putting them on upside down,
And there was one from the court with orders for me.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
