      <prop type="x-translation-ref">東方未明.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>折柳樊圃，狂夫瞿瞿。不能辰夜，不夙則莫。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>You fence your garden with branches of willow,
And the reckless fellows stand in awe.
He, however, cannot fix the time of night;
If he be not too early, he is sure to be late.</seg>
      </tuv>
